[Final Fight Codes\Boss Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=Might make it to where you can't advance or fight the enemy, depending on what stage & what character you use. Unfortunately, normal enemies can't be used as bosses.
Values - 
00 - Damn'd
01 - Sodom
02 - Edi E.
03 - Rolento
04 - Abigail
05 - Belger
