[SFII Hyper Fighting Codes\P1 Rapid Fire Punches & Kicks]
author=BigBossman
description=Basically, its like auto fire or having a controller with turbo buttons. Just hold down any button & you keep attacking. This also makes it much easier for Blanka to do a Fierce Electric Attack, E. Honda to do a Fierce Hundred Hand Slap, & Chun-Li to do a Roundhouse Lightning Leg Kick.
patch=1,EE,006087AA,extended,00000001

