[Final Fight Codes\Player 1 Auto Grab]
author=BigBossman
description=Allows you to grab enemies without having to get too close to them. It will also make your standing attacks ineffective against enemies.
patch=1,EE,00CDB012,extended,00000001
patch=1,EE,00CDB013,extended,00000001

[Street Fighter II Codes\Player 1 Color Set Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=These codes change the entire palette set for each player. Some look better on some characters than others. I've indicated which set looks the best on which character with each value.
Values - 
01 - No change in appearance
02 - E. Honda (normal) / M. Bison / Vega / Blanka / Guile (Turbo Edition?) / Sagat
03 - Blanka (normal) / Ryu / Ken / E. Honda / Sagat (orange) / M. Bison / Vega
04 - Guile (normal) / M. Bison (normal)
05 - Ken (normal) / Ryu / E. Honda / Blanka / Guile / Sagat / M. Bison (with green shin & shoulder guards)
06 - Chun-Li (normal) / E. Honda
07 - Zangief (normal)
08 - Dhalsim (normal) / Balrog
09 - Shadow characters
0B - Ryu / Ken / Vega / Sagat / Blanka / E. Honda / Guile
0E - Sagat / Ryu / Ken
patch=1,EE,005D4EB0,extended,00000000

[SFII Champion Edition Codes\Player 1 Color Set Modifier]
author=BigBossman
