[Final Fight Codes\Player 1 Front Auto Attack]
author=BigBossman
description=All you have to do is face enemies & objects up close they will take damage. Most enemies will keep taking damage until they die (including bosses), others will block. Those that jump will be knocked out of the air. You'll also damage enemies even when you are knocked down. This only works when you are facing enemies or objects mostly when standing still.
patch=1,EE,00CDB005,extended,00000002

