[Street Fighter II Codes\Stage & CPU Opponent Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=When playing a one player game, you will always fight the same opponent on the same stage all the time. It is possible to fight on the bonus stages, when a second player joins in. Fighting against the CPU in bonus areas is possible if this code is paired with a joker code. It will need to be activated during the Vs Screen. If it is activated too soon, the plane on the map will fly to Player 1's picture & the game will freeze.
Values - 
00 - Ryu / Japan
01 - E. Honda / Japan
02 - Blanka / Brazil
03 - Guile / USA
04 - Ken / USA
05 - Chun-Li / China
06 - Zangief / USSR
07 - Dhalsim / India
08 - M. Bison / Thailand
09 - Sagat / Thailand
0A - Balrog / USA
0B - Vega / Spain
0C - Car Bonus Stage
0D - Wooden Barrel Bonus Stage
0E - Flaming Barrel Bonus Stage
patch=1,EE,005D5170,extended,00000000

