[Street Fighter II Codes\Starting Stage Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=This just modifies where you start in the game. For example, if you use value "08", you'll start the game fighting Balrog & advance to fighting Vega, then Sagat, & finally M. Bison. Using values "00" to "07" will generate a random stage & proceed from that point.
Values -
00 - 1st Fight
01 - 2nd Fight
02 - 3rd Fight
03 - 4th Fight
04 - 5th Fight
05 - 6th Fight
06 - 7th Fight
07 - 8th Fight
08 - Fight against Balrog
09 - Fight against Vega
0A - Fight against Sagat
0B - Fight against M. Bison
patch=1,EE,005D5172,extended,00000000

