[Street Fighter II Codes\Vega's Claw Modifier - Player 1]
author=BigBossman
description=With Value "00" active, it Vega's claw won't be seen, but will make the slashing sound when opponents are hit.
Values - 
00 - Always invisible
01 - Always visible
